# AI Prompts Log

## 1. Initial MVP Prompt

Used to generate the first version of the game UI.

Build a mobile-first EVM game application with simple wallet connection using MetaMask and Rabby.

The app should be a single-page interface with a large central number showing the current money pot in USD.

Under the pot, include one main button: “Add Money”.

Game concept:
Users can add funds to the shared pot. The objective is to be the user who makes the total pot reach an exact full million-dollar milestone, such as $1,000,000, $2,000,000, $3,000,000, and so on.

If a user adds an amount that makes the pot exactly reach the next million-dollar milestone, that user wins $1,000,000.

If the contribution causes the pot to go over the current million-dollar milestone, no one wins and the game continues toward the next million-dollar milestone.

Example:
Current pot: $999,999.99
User adds: $0.01
New pot: $1,000,000.00
This user wins $1,000,000.

The remaining funds stay in the contract and continue supporting the next million-dollar round.

Design requirements:
- Mobile-first
- One-page layout
- Big bold pot number
- Simple and clean UI
- Clear wallet connection
- Clear “Add Money” button
- Show current target milestone
- Show last contributor
- Show winner history
- Make the game feel exciting, simple, and viral

Smart contract requirements:
- EVM-compatible
- Wallet connection with MetaMask and Rabby
- Transparent pot balance
- Track each contribution
- Detect when the pot reaches an exact million-dollar milestone
- Automatically assign the winner
- Keep the remaining pot active for future milestones
- Include basic security protections against exploits


